{"title":"哭吴世昌先生","authors":["冯其庸"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":9,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭吴世昌先生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冯其庸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传来噩耗忒心惊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦幻迷离怕是真。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽忆春前同语笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照人肝胆即先生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高楼犹记识荆初，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披胆相倾各皎如。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意气由来重一诺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"校红七载未曾疏。＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从来世路最崎岖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"误中阱罗喜螫蛛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自有文章光万丈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千秋犹作夜光珠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翰墨追随老伏波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红坛尚欲仰雕戈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知摧折南山树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我长宵泪似沱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊先生曾任《红楼梦》校注组顾问，前后七年，未尝中辍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九八六年九月六日夜二时"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}